Package CarPark

CarPark is a set of classes that represent a car park ecosystem

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CarParkManager
    Interface that incorporates the main functionality that has to be implemented by a car park manager
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CarPark
    Class that represents an entire car park ecosystem
    CarParkTest
    Junit4 Testing class that test the main functionality of the CarPark class.
    DatabaseHandler
    Class that incorporates the Database handling functionalities
    DatabaseHandlerTest
    Junit4 Testing class that test the main functionality of the DatabaseHandler class.
    Floor
    Class that is used to represent each floor level used in the CarPark class
    FloorTest
    Junit4 Test class that tests the main functionalities of the Floor class
    IITCarParkTesting
    Junit4 Testing class that test the vehicles are added to the correct floor of the CarPark class.
